{"tid":1251524,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"依加焦點應該放係 限制警權度   而唔係「撤回」","createTime":"2019-06-22T14:30:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T06:19:14.000Z","uid":96540,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"de0fe27f8b3e3dff43fc896c0cca0a85f3894a44","tid":1251524,"uid":96540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T14:30:35.000Z","msg":"明白無講出「撤回」 個感覺好似輸左咁<br />\n但其實應該都真係唔會推行修例<br />\n情況同國教差不多 就算日後再推<br />\n要聚集返反對既聲音都唔難<br />\n<br />\n因為日日都咁多on9新聞出現<br />\n好易<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">失焦</span></span><br />\n令到反對聲音分散 政府警隊輕鬆過骨<br />\n<br />\n所以集合處理警權既事較好<br />\n試諗諗 警隊荒謬既事係多到<br />\n黎緊幾年投考人數應該都會下降<br />\n咁人工會上升 所以叫人唔好做基本上都無乜可能<br />\n<br />\n所以<span style=\"color: red;\">獨立委員會</span>係必須<br />\n成個警隊改革都係必須<br />\n好似當年ICAC既出現咁 必須有樣野去制衡返個警權<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39c9f4d5c11777a80870b1afcbe219e51f286580","tid":1251524,"uid":7954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T14:31:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c474c1dd287250140424ab69c62f6119033f445","tid":1251524,"uid":231040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T06:19:14.000Z","msg":"[反送中] 一圖講哂「撤回」同「暫緩」嘅分別<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1254409\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1254409</a>"}]}